mostly by hand.

268
0:11:45.26,000 --> 0:11:48,000
It was chaos.

269
0:11:48.26,000 --> 0:11:51,000
And the Balinese carpenters want to be as modern as we do,

270
0:11:51.26,000 --> 0:11:54,000
so they use metal scaffolding

271
0:11:54.26,000 --> 0:11:57,000
to build the bamboo building

272
0:11:57.26,000 --> 0:12:,000
