274
0:12:05.26,000 --> 0:12:07,000
a cathedral to green,

275
0:12:07.26,000 --> 0:12:1,000
and a cathedral to green education.

276
0:12:10.26,000 --> 0:12:12,000
The heart of school has seven kilometers

277
0:12:12.26,000 --> 0:12:14,000
of bamboo in it.

278
0:12:14.26,000 --> 0:12:16,000
From the time the foundations were finished,

